synopsis: An atheist goes on a pilgrimage to Sabarimala. What will he get out of the experience? The film features Biju Menon and Nimisha Sajayan in the lead roles and was shot in Thalaserry.
casting: ['Biju Menon', 'Sharanjith', 'Nimisha Sajayan', 'Dhanya Ananya', 'Suresh Krishna', 'Indrans', 'Shivaji Guruvayoor', 'V. T. Vijilesh']
